document.full_text: the "no" vote was ahead in early returns on sunday in iceland's referendum on a plan to repay britain and the netherlands $5 billion from a bank crash, a deal that is seen as key to iceland's swift economic recovery.
document.title: "no" vote ahead in iceland debt deal referendum
